summary: I finally got to watch Avengers: Infinity War! And oh my goodness, what the hell was I thinking? I even knew how it would end...
body: I finally got to watch Avengers: Infinity War! And oh my goodness, what the hell was I thinking? I even knew how it would end (thanks Internet but did try to avoid spoilers as much as possible and not one to avoid talking about them either, hence the tag #spoilers sweetie) and it still got me. Why do I do this to myself? But that aside, it genuinely was an awesome movie. Not as funny as Thor: Ragnorok but it had it’s moments and definitely going for the dramatic as always.

summary: Steve Rogers is America's version of Naruto
body:
Steve Rogers is America’s version of Naruto

  • Both stayed a low rank for a long period of time even though they deserved to be promoted
  • Both were severely underestimated until they were given access to superhuman abilities
  • Both saved their friends and countrymen several times with stealth and badass combat skills
  • Both lost their best friend to the dark side
  • Both managed to save their friends by beating the shit out of them
  • Both had to choose between following the rules or sticking to their values
  • Both chose to stick to their values
  • Both are blonde
  • Both grew up being kicked around
  • Both grew up in bad parts of town

body:
Masa Depan Chris Evans hingga Robert Downey Jr Pasca Avengers Kata Marvel

[ad_1]





Jakarta –

Peristiwa ‘Avengers: Infinity War’ juga ‘Avengers 4’ direncanakan sebagai momen yang akan membawa perubahan pada Marvel Cinematic Universe.

Bos Marvel, Kevin Feige telah mengkonfirmasi bahwa sekuelnya pasti akan menjadi akhir dari sebuah era. Captain Marvel kemudian menjadi wajah baru menggantikan sosok Captain America dan Iron Man.

Yang membuat penggemar bertanya-tanya,…
